Package: SimpleGridder
Type: Package
Title: A simple utility for (re)gridding observational data.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Thomas Kelly
Maintainer: Thomas Kelly <tbkelly@alaska.edu>
Description: This package is to facilitate the interpolation/extrapolation/binning of irregularly spaced observational data onto a reguarl grid. Tools include multiple interpolators and simple, base-graphics plotting routines that are easily adapted.
License: MIT License
Encoding: UTF-8
